Package org.ensembl.compara.datamodel

Data types that are unique to ensembl compara databases such as Homology and GenomicAlign.

Interface Summary
ComparaDataFactory Abstract Factory for creating ensembl data objects.

Family I represent a single species which is part of the compara- analyses.
GenomeDB I represent a single species which is part of the compara- analyses.
GenomicAlign I am part of the compara-analysis.
GenomicAlignBlock I am part of the compara-analysis.
Homology I represent a single species which is part of the compara- analyses.
Member I represent a single species which is part of the compara- analyses.
MethodLink I represent a type of dna-dna alignment
MethodLinkSpeciesSet I represent a type of analysis which could be applied between the elements of a set of genomes and the actual set which had it applied.
